If you put a number in for a fraction of a turn,

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:51.040
and it is a fraction.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.500
i.e. has a denominator,

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:53.440
it's going to give you spokes.

