But there are other irrational numbers.

00:05:24.500 --> 00:05:26.020
I'm gonna type in 1/Pi,

00:05:26.020 --> 00:05:27.460
because Pi is a lot of peoples favourite

00:05:27.460 --> 00:05:28.320
irrational number.

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:29.280
This surprised me.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:30.180
Think about what you might see.

00:05:30.180 --> 00:05:32.214
We know it can't produce spokes because

