Pi is irrational.

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:34.300
Now they're not quite spokes,

00:05:34.300 --> 00:05:35.440
but they're slightly curved spokes,

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:37.300
and there are in fact 22 of them,

