And I'll show it to you,

00:06:26.020 --> 00:06:27.000
and I'll show you why.

00:06:27.020 --> 00:06:27.860
So, here it is.

00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:30.800
If I jump to the square root of 5, minus 1, over 2,

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:31.680
you get this.

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:33.340
This is the golden ratio of the turn,

00:06:33.340 --> 00:06:34.240
and what's lovely about it

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.240
is you can see spokes,

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.660
but you can see them going in both directions.

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:38.060
They're kind of crossing over both ways.

00:06:38.060 --> 00:06:39.220
