00:06:39.220 --> 00:06:40.820
and if you do, you get fibbonaci numbers.

00:06:40.820 --> 00:06:42.540
And if you go and look in the real world,

00:06:42.540 --> 00:06:44.040
this is the bit that a lot of people claim

