So if I hide the seeds there,

00:06:47.180 --> 00:06:48.380
that's the arrangement of seeds

00:06:48.380 --> 00:06:49.420
in the head of a sunflower.

00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:50.740
That's not generated by a computer.

